        </div>

        <div class="inline-cta">
          <div class="cta-copy">
            <h4>Stop juggling writer + tool + CMS.</h4>
            <p>theStacc handles topic research, briefs, writing, optimisation, and publishing to WordPress / Webflow / Ghost. <strong>30 articles/month for $99</strong> — one subscription, zero coordination.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cta-action">
            <a href="/demo/" class="cta-btn-inline">See a live demo <span>→</span></a>
            <span class="cta-meta">No card · 15-min walkthrough</span>
