          <li><strong>Brief generation</strong> — outline, H2s, FAQs, internal-link targets.</li>
          <li><strong>Writing</strong> — drafts the article matched to brand voice and SERP intent.</li>
          <li><strong>SEO optimisation</strong> — keyword density, semantic terms, meta, schema.</li>
          <li><strong>Publishing</strong> — pushes to WordPress / Webflow / Ghost on a schedule.</li>
        </ol>

